I think this is due to [line 719 in Decimal128.cs|https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-csharp-driver/blob/master/src/MongoDB.Bson/ObjectModel/Decimal128.cs#L719]:
{code:csharp} if (Decimal128.IsZero(d))
